{"title":"The Haro Buzzard Gravel Bike","link":"https://theradavist.com/haro-buzzard-gravel-bike/","date":1716555614000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1772\" height=\"1182\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Masi-CXGR-Beauty-Shots-4-1.jpg?fit=1200,1182&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Masi-CXGR-Beauty-Shots-4-1.jpg?w=1772&amp;quality=75 1772w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Masi-CXGR-Beauty-Shots-4-1.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Masi-CXGR-Beauty-Shots-4-1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Masi-CXGR-Beauty-Shots-4-1.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><em>The <a href=\"https://harobikes.com/collections/gravel\" target=\"_blank\">Haro Buzzard</a> is a carbon chassis gravel platform with builds starting at $2,999.99 and all the features found in much more expensive bikes. Let’s take a look.</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2200\" height=\"1467\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/2024-Haro-Buzzard-Carbon-3-Black.jpg?fit=1200,1467&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/2024-Haro-Buzzard-Carbon-3-Black.jpg?w=2200&amp;quality=75 2200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/2024-Haro-Buzzard-Carbon-3-Black.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/2024-Haro-Buzzard-Carbon-3-Black.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/2024-Haro-Buzzard-Carbon-3-Black.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/2024-Haro-Buzzard-Carbon-3-Black.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/2024-Haro-Buzzard-Carbon-3-Black.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Haro’s Buzzard is a versatile carbon gravel bike has a long front triangle for stability and a short rear end with flared chain stays that make it easy to whip through tight terrain, making for an incredibly nimble ride feel. It features in-frame downtube storage and 18 mounts accommodate racks, fenders and panniers for multi-day adventure rides.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2200\" height=\"1467\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/2024-Haro-Buzzard-Carbon-3-Black-1.jpg?fit=1200,1467&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/2024-Haro-Buzzard-Carbon-3-Black-1.jpg?w=2200&amp;quality=75 2200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/2024-Haro-Buzzard-Carbon-3-Black-1.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/2024-Haro-Buzzard-Carbon-3-Black-1.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/2024-Haro-Buzzard-Carbon-3-Black-1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/2024-Haro-Buzzard-Carbon-3-Black-1.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/2024-Haro-Buzzard-Carbon-3-Black-1.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>There’s internal cable routing, UDH compatibility and space for wide tires (up to a 45 mm in the rear) thanks to the dropped chainstay, make the Buzzard sleek and functional. With a Shimano GRX group, Vision Team Aero Gravel alloy tubeless wheels and Vittoria Terreno Dry gravel tires, it will get you in the gravel groove.</p>\n<p>Check out the Buzzard builds at <a href=\"https://harobikes.com/collections/gravel\" target=\"_blank\">Haro</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/haro-buzzard-gravel-bike/\">The Haro Buzzard Gravel Bike</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"8218f92babfe1992a51bd9ed4ff19034694a751a3c24344ebd202e63b79d8cb7","category":"Cycling"}